00:02:01.635 --> 00:02:03.650
ODED BEN DOV: It's not
a standard company.

00:02:03.650 --> 00:02:06.110
You have days when you're
crying from happiness,

00:02:06.110 --> 00:02:08.910
because you really, really
touched the person's life.

00:02:08.910 --> 00:02:10.880
With the app now
being on Google Play,

00:02:10.880 --> 00:02:12.570
anyone can download
it around the world,

00:02:12.570 --> 00:02:14.500
and we're seeing that.

00:02:14.500 --> 00:02:17.260
One of our greatest
users is Alex Friedman.

00:02:17.260 --> 00:02:20.110
I met him on social
circles, and at the time,

00:02:20.110 --> 00:02:23.350
he was just starting a
campaign to raise awareness

00:02:23.350 --> 00:02:24.940
around disabilities in Israel.

00:02:24.940 --> 00:02:27.085
And he uses Sesame remarkably.

00:02:47.440 --> 00:02:52.032
SPEAKER 2: It's fun, because we
can communicate all day long.

00:02:52.032 --> 00:02:56.780
ALEX FRIEDMAN: [INAUDIBLE]

00:02:56.780 --> 00:02:59.480
ODED BEN DOV: Google Play
Console gives us a lot of tools

00:02:59.480 --> 00:03:01.640
to care for our users better.

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:03.892
We see what's working
right and what's not.

00:03:03.892 --> 00:03:05.350
Through the ratings
and reviews, we

00:03:05.350 --> 00:03:07.150
can actually be in
touch with users

00:03:07.150 --> 00:03:08.900
and take benefits from
all the great stuff

00:03:08.900 --> 00:03:10.930
the Play Store offers.

00:03:10.930 --> 00:03:12.850
I think the biggest
takeaway from Sesame

00:03:12.850 --> 00:03:14.350
is the lives you touch.

00:03:14.350 --> 00:03:17.960
Every successful user
is not just a number.

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:18.880
It's a whole life.

00:03:18.880 --> 00:03:21.310
It's a whole story.

00:03:21.310 --> 00:03:24.110
And we take those with us,
and those propel us forward

00:03:24.110 --> 00:03:25.240
to keep doing what we do.

